name: Beautiful
description: Beautiful is a radiant, harmonizing piece, helping us focus on all that is beautiful and balanced in ourselves and in our environment.  When you hang Beautiful in your space it can inspire you toward the best goals you have for yourself. This is a wonderful piece to give as a gift in any occasion.

name: Totem
description: Totem is a power piece with intention; to intensify energies needed to reach the goals we have set for ourselves. Totem as a large print alone on a wall of an office space, business meeting center or attorney's office can energetically facilitate accomplishment of goals.  At home you probably want to have a smaller print as it packs a powerful charge.

name: What flavor Are You?
description: What Flavor Are You signifies the playful, interpersonal and sensual aspects of ourselves.  When was the last time you played?  This piece will remind you in case you forget, that you are unique, irreplaceable flavor that is needed to make the delicious creation that is humanity. Make it a priority to display and share your flavor. Hang this Prayer in a bedroom or any other space that is used for socializing and fun.

name: The Ring
description: The Ring is a remainder of all the promises and commitments that we've made in the past and continue to make as we travel on our individual paths.  The Ring reminds us of the beauty of honoring our commitments starting with the commitment we make for ourselves to love and honor all that is I.  From loving ourselves and honoring the commitments we've made for ourselves we can honor the commitments we've made to others with grace and humility. The Ring will help to balance vibration in a work space or study room facilitating calm, balanced attitude regarding responsibilities and commitments in our lives.

name: Karma
description: This piece connects us with our past, present and future with the focus on all that we are, have been and will be.  Keeping that which celebrates and supports all that we hold dear in our essence while courageously standing our ground resisting all that is not in our best interest.  Karma symbolizes the all knowing aspect of ourselves that has complete understanding of cause and effect. Viewer will take a moment to unconsciously process where they are right now in their process of standing firm to do no harm to self or to others.  Karma will balance any environment except the bedroom or child's room.  Karma is a beautiful piece to greet visitors in an entry way.
